Building lsxinic module:
==============================

Build
------
$ cd lsxinic
$ export DPDKDIR=/path/to/custom/dpdk/source
# Cross build for ARM64 RC:
$ make KSRC=/path/to/custom/kernel/source CROSS_COMPILE=aarch64-linux-gnu- ARCH=arm64
# Native build:
$ make

The .ko file will be generated, which can be loaded using after EP application is loaded:
$ insmod lsinic_kmod.ko

Clean
------
To clean the build directory, the following command can be run:

$ cd lsxinic
$ make clean
